title: The Culture Corner: Get to know Cody ChesnuTT, the writer behind The Roots' 'The Seed'
description: On today's edition of The Culture Corner, World Cafe Correspondent John Morrison talks about that song and dives deep into Cody's 2002 album, The Headphone Masterpiece.
